Irène Tunc https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ir%C3%A8ne_Tunc 0 Irène Tunc (25 September 1935 – 16 January 1972) was a French actress and model. She was crowned Miss France in 1954. She was the wife of film director Alain Cavalier and she died in a car crash in 1972. She appeared in 35 films and television shows between 1955 and 1971.
